msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/8.x/eloquent.md:79
msgid ""
"Models generated by the `make:model` command will be placed in the "
"`app/Models` directory. Let's examine a basic model class and discuss some "
"of Eloquent's key conventions:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
